title: Battalion 609
subTitle: Indian and Pakistani armies clash verbally, leading to a cricket match challenge where territorial pride hangs in the balance.

title: 3I 3 Indians
subTitle: Raj, Shahan and Sherdill join a covert operation led by a reformist minister to expose dangerous networks that threaten the country from within.

title: Shool
subTitle: Inspector Samar is transferred to Motihari in Bihar, India, due to his honesty. He soon earns the wrath of a corrupt politician, Bachchu Yadav, who gradually becomes a threat to him and his family.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: When Birju's sister, Chhaya, is raped and the court fails to mete out justice, his parents die due to the shock. Birju sets out to seek revenge and kidnaps Dinanath's sister.

title: Karamdaata
subTitle: Pinky, the granddaughter of a wealthy industrialist, runs away and marries a taxi driver. However, the businessman holds Pinky's lover responsible and gets him arrested.

title: Satta
subTitle: Anuradha relocates to Mumbai where she meets Vivek, an aspiring politician, and marries him. Things take a turn when he is arrested for murder and she has to take his place in the upcoming elections.

title: Bollywood Diaries
subTitle: Three individuals from different backgrounds aspire to make it big in Bollywood but face difficulties as they carve their path.

title: Gone Kesh
subTitle: After being diagnosed with alopecia, a condition that causes rapid hair loss, Enakshi, a young girl, navigates through the trials and tribulations of life.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Soldier
subTitle: After Major Vijay Malhotra's colleagues betray him, he is branded as a traitor and subsequently killed. But his son, Vicky, vows to take revenge on his father's murderers and prove his innocence.

title: Dosti: Friends Forever
subTitle: Karan, a wealthy heir, lives a lonely life and is neglected by his family. When he has a fatal accident, Raj, a poor orphan, saves his life and they become inseparable friends.

title: Dosti: Friends Forever
subTitle: Karan, a wealthy heir, lives a lonely life and is neglected by his family. When he has a fatal accident, Raj, a poor orphan, saves his life and they become inseparable friends.

title: Shakalaka Boom Boom
subTitle: Reggie, an aspiring singer, faces fierce opposition from an established musician determined to sabotage his career out of personal revenge.

title: Deewana Tere Naam Ka
subTitle: Friends Shankar and Shambhu share a lot in common and also end up falling in love with the same girl. However, when the girl loves Shankar, Shambhu parts ways with him and joins his rival.

title: Vinashak - Destroyer
subTitle: A diligent and determined police officer is tasked with uncovering the truth behind a crooked warden involved in illicit weapon trafficking.

title: Kaun Sachcha Kaun Jhootha
subTitle: Karan Saxena, a police officer, arrests Sapna Mathur, a woman accused of killing his fellow constable. Things take a turn when Karan falls in love with her and helps her escape her death sentence.

title: Aag
subTitle: A young man seeks a fresh start in a village after enduring tragedy, only to find himself entangled in a conflict that tests his strength and sense of justice.

title: Dariya Dil
subTitle: A wealthy tycoon's clash with a tax officer sparks a sinister plot, as the official's siblings scheme to pilfer the businessman's fortune.

title: Champion
subTitle: Rajveer, a police officer, is tasked with protecting a nine-year-old heir, Abbas. However, the job gets complicated when Nazir, a dangerous criminal, seeks to harm the child.

title: Lootere
subTitle: Police inspectors Karan and Ali investigate the murder of a colleague, Inspector Rane. Karan takes the responsibility of protecting Anjali, a bar dancer who is a key witness to the crime.

title: Lootere
subTitle: Police inspectors Karan and Ali investigate the murder of a colleague, Inspector Rane. Karan takes the responsibility of protecting Anjali, a bar dancer who is a key witness to the crime.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Phamous
subTitle: Radhe looks up to Kadak Singh, a local politician, but holds a grudge against his partner, Ram Tripathi. However, things reach a boiling point when Tripathi sets his sights on Radhe's wife, Lalli.

title: Raja Saab
subTitle: Upon Prince Pratap's insistence, Rajoo impersonates him in front of Princess Poonam. But the imitation lands him in trouble when she starts falling for Rajoo, unaware of his poor background.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Gair Kaanooni
subTitle: Police Inspector Kapil Khanna realises that his baby boy has been switched with a girl child by the hospital and files a lawsuit against the owner, Robert Decosta while trying to find his missing son.

title: Ekka Raja Rani
subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

title: I M 24
subTitle: A 42-year-old writer falls in love with a 22-year-old beauty queen. However, things get complicated when his roommate encourages him to make up stories to impress her.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Albela
subTitle: A woman gets stuck in India when her flight to a foreign country gets delayed. While travelling in India, she meets Tony, a tour guide, and things take a turn when he falls in love with her.
